data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is located in the area of Buena Vista and is move in ready. It features a 2-car garage with a drive through to the backyard to store your toys. Fenced in front and backyard with beautiful views from the front yard. New heat pump 3 years old. ADT alarm system. Located close the grocery store, bank, restaurant, hospital and bus line.
